<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>扩展性 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E6%80%A7/</link><description>扩展性 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E6%80%A7/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>多平台架构设计</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="多平台架构设计">多平台架构设计</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：多平台架构通过抽象公共层复用核心能力，通过配置化区分平台差异，通过插件化机制支持平台特有扩展，避免为每个平台独立开发一套系统。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="多平台架构通过公共层复用配置化差异插件化扩展实现一套代码支撑多端">多平台架构通过公共层复用、配置化差异、插件化扩展实现一套代码支撑多端</h2>
<h3 id="架构分层">架构分层</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">接入层（各平台独立）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── Web端（React/Vue）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── App端（iOS/Android）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── 小程序（微信/支付宝）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└── H5
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        ↓ 统一API网关
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">业务中台（公共能力）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── 用户中心
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── 订单中心
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── 支付中心
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└── 消息中心
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        ↓ 平台配置
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">平台适配层
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── 平台配置（开关、文案、页面编排）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">├── 差异化逻辑（不同平台不同实现）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">└── 插件扩展点</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="配置化设计">配置化设计</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-yaml">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c"># 平台配置</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nt">platform</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">  </span><span class="nt">ios</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">payment_channels</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">[</span><span class="l">apple_pay, alipay, wechat]</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">features</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span><span class="nt">live_stream</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">true</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span><span class="nt">gift_combo</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">true</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">  </span><span class="nt">android</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">payment_channels</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">[</span><span class="l">alipay, wechat]</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">features</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span><span class="nt">live_stream</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">true</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span><span class="nt">gift_combo</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">false</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">  </span><span class="nt">web</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">payment_channels</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">[</span><span class="l">alipay, wechat]</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="nt">features</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">      </span><span class="nt">live_stream</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kc">false</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1平台差异代码散落在各处">问题1：平台差异代码散落在各处</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：缺乏统一的适配层
<strong>解决</strong>：集中平台判断逻辑，使用策略模式</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>